<div class="lang-en">
<section id="luck-pillars">
  <h2>Luck Pillars (<span class="chinese-char">大運</span>)</h2>
  <p>Your birth chart is fixed, but time moves. <strong>Luck Pillars</strong> (Dà Yùn, <span class="chinese-char">大運</span>) are ten-year periods that each bring a new Stem-Branch combination into your life. They function like a changing backdrop against which your fixed chart plays out.</p>
  <p>Each Luck Pillar introduces new elements that interact with your birth chart. A favourable Luck Pillar brings elements that balance your chart &mdash; these tend to be your best decades. An unfavourable one amplifies your chart's weaknesses &mdash; these are periods that require caution and adaptation.</p>
  <p>Annual pillars (the Stem-Branch of each year, like 2026's Bǐngwǔ) add a further layer of timing. A good year within a difficult decade can still yield positive results; a bad year within a favourable decade is usually manageable. This layered timing system is what gives BaZi its predictive nuance.</p>
</section>
</div>
<div class="lang-tc">
<section id="luck-pillars">
  <h2>大運（<span class="chinese-char">大運</span>）</h2>
  <p>你的命盤是固定的，但時間在流動。<strong>大運</strong>（Dà Yùn，<span class="chinese-char">大運</span>）是每十年一個週期，每個大運帶來一組新的干支組合進入你的人生。它們猶如不斷變換的背景，你的固定命盤在其上演繹。</p>
  <p>每個大運引入新的五行元素，與你的命盤互動。有利的大運帶來平衡命盤的元素——這些往往是你最好的十年。不利的大運則放大命盤的弱點——這些時期需要謹慎和調適。</p>
  <p>流年（每年的干支，如2026年的丙午）增加了更細緻的時間層次。困難大運中遇到好的流年仍可取得正面成果；有利大運中遇到不好的流年通常也能應對。這種層層疊加的時間體系賦予了八字預測的精微之處。</p>
</section>
</div>
<div class="lang-sc">
<section id="luck-pillars">
  <h2>大运（<span class="chinese-char">大運</span>）</h2>
  <p>你的命盘是固定的，但时间在流动。<strong>大运</strong>（Dà Yùn，<span class="chinese-char">大運</span>）是每十年一个周期，每个大运带来一组新的干支组合进入你的人生。它们犹如不断变换的背景，你的固定命盘在其上演绎。</p>
  <p>每个大运引入新的五行元素，与你的命盘互动。有利的大运带来平衡命盘的元素——这些往往是你最好的十年。不利的大运则放大命盘的弱点——这些时期需要谨慎和调适。</p>
  <p>流年（每年的干支，如2026年的丙午）增加了更细致的时间层次。困难大运中遇到好的流年仍可取得正面成果；有利大运中遇到不好的流年通常也能应对。这种层层叠加的时间体系赋予了八字预测的精微之处。</p>
</section>
</div>

<div class="lang-en">
<section id="step-by-step">
  <h2>Reading Your Chart: Step by Step</h2>
  <p>Here is a simplified process for reading a BaZi chart. Generate your chart using the <a href="/bazi-calculator/">BaZi Calculator</a>, then follow these steps:</p>
  <p><strong>Step 1 &mdash; Identify your Day Master.</strong> Look at the Heavenly Stem of your Day Pillar. This is your core element. Note whether it is yin or yang.</p>
  <p><strong>Step 2 &mdash; Count elements.</strong> List every element across all eight characters (four Stems + four Branches, including hidden stems). Tally Wood, Fire, Earth, Metal, and Water.</p>
  <p><strong>Step 3 &mdash; Assess Day Master strength.</strong> Is your Day Master element well-supported (appears frequently, has elements that produce it)? Or is it isolated and pressured by controlling elements? This determines whether your Day Master is "strong" or "weak."</p>
  <p><strong>Step 4 &mdash; Identify favourable elements.</strong> A strong Day Master benefits from elements that drain or control it (output and wealth). A weak Day Master benefits from elements that produce or support it (resource and companion). This is the most critical assessment in basic BaZi.</p>
  <p><strong>Step 5 &mdash; Read the Ten Gods.</strong> Label each character by its Ten God relationship to your Day Master. Note which gods appear most frequently &mdash; these dominate your chart's themes.</p>
  <p><strong>Step 6 &mdash; Check for combinations and clashes.</strong> Certain Branch pairs combine (producing new elements) or clash (creating conflict). These modify the element count from Step 2 and can change the chart's balance significantly.</p>
  <p><strong>Step 7 &mdash; Examine Luck Pillars.</strong> Look at which elements your current and upcoming Luck Pillars bring. Are they favourable or unfavourable based on your Step 4 assessment?</p>
</section>
</div>
<div class="lang-tc">
<section id="step-by-step">
  <h2>解讀命盤：逐步指引</h2>
  <p>以下是解讀八字命盤的簡化流程。請先使用<a href="/bazi-calculator/">八字計算器</a>生成你的命盤，然後按照以下步驟操作：</p>
  <p><strong>第一步——辨識日主。</strong>查看日柱的天干，這就是你的核心元素。注意它是陰還是陽。</p>
  <p><strong>第二步——統計五行。</strong>列出八個字（四天干加四地支，包括藏干）中的所有元素。分別統計木、火、土、金、水的數量。</p>
  <p><strong>第三步——判斷日主強弱。</strong>你的日主元素是否得到充分支持（出現頻率高，有生扶它的元素）？還是孤立無援，受克制元素壓制？這決定了日主是「身旺」還是「身弱」。</p>
  <p><strong>第四步——確定喜用元素。</strong>身旺的日主受益於洩耗或克制它的元素（食傷和財星）。身弱的日主受益於生扶它的元素（印星和比劫）。這是基礎八字中最關鍵的判斷。</p>
  <p><strong>第五步——解讀十神。</strong>根據與日主的十神關係為每個字標注標籤。注意哪些十神出現最多——它們主導你命盤的主題。</p>
  <p><strong>第六步——檢查合化與沖克。</strong>某些地支之間會合化（產生新元素）或相沖（產生衝突）。這會改變第二步中的五行統計，並可能顯著改變命盤的平衡。</p>
  <p><strong>第七步——審視大運。</strong>查看當前和未來的大運帶來哪些元素。根據第四步的判斷，它們是喜用還是忌神？</p>
</section>
</div>
